  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial will evaluate the efficacy in colon cleansing of a nurse-led educational telephone
      intervention 24-48 hours before a colonoscopy, in selected participants with a previous
      inadequate bowel preparation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
